{
  "stem": "3382.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, shoot me the way I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What is the matter with you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are you afraid?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am not afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Turn around you, [SPEAKING GERMAN] whatever or not, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the time, I was a Pole, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] He, he came up to me, you know, and hit me with the butt of the revolver, knocking out upper teeth, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I felt everything gets warm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I spit out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to him, oh, you can tell-- it is-- it is a very clean work-- job, I said.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can tell Colonel Haushoffer that you knocked out teeth from Mielzynski's mouth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, Haushoffer?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Haushoffer?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I go, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I felt that, you know, I'm getting a little bit such-- you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Haushoffer was the famous German professor who made the geopolitik, you know, the theoretician.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I just spoke out, without thinking specially of something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he started to hit me with the revolver, with his legs, and whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, when I woke up-- so I, I dreamed that I am swimming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By the way, I don't know how to swim.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, so I was somewhere in the corner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a German put-- threw on me water-- get up!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Get up!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Get up!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I returned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My number was 32,209.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We went through Stutthof.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I got to a very big block-- barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there, I felt that, you know, there was one-- a former petty officer from Polish Navy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the moment he knew that we're intelligentsia-- so he tried to do everything what he could to maltreat us.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
